{"tid":790304,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好懷念以前麥樂勞兒童樂園餐嘅玩具","createTime":"2018-08-23T02:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T08:49:24.000Z","uid":34777,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0f07aa064f60f86179b616441908b93d684838a9","tid":790304,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:11:29.000Z","msg":"見有po講嗰啲小朋友玩具<br />\n令我諗番起以前麥當勞出咗隻比小朋友發揮創意嘅玩具<br />\n利用唔同嘅膠條棒去砌出唔同嘅遊樂設施比嗰四大天王玩<br />\n記得細個嗰陣狂食係咁儲啲棒去砌更多唔同嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個玩具我到依家屋企仲有keep<br />\n真係覺得好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人都玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲成本唔太高嘅玩具都唔明點解唔再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走去出埋啲咩圖書 得個擺字嘅垃圾公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/101001_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F101001_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=77967e6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fb9c662ee7bde5167ad0133cbcabf0d78adf615","tid":790304,"uid":34777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:14:07.000Z","msg":"屌 唔小心打錯標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a00bffa234fc46bcba2cb84b20d0874bbf1edbb","tid":790304,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人玩過？<br />\n好好玩架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1883d65dc2559fc34d3d5b031fe507660cf23fd5","tid":790304,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a00bffa234fc46bcba2cb84b20d0874bbf1edbb","tid":790304,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人玩過？<br />\n好好玩架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"依家得啲00後上連登，係咁架啦"},{"pid":"112c2abba951fec3fc6b030b6171cf77c3d60bee","tid":790304,"uid":34777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1883d65dc2559fc34d3d5b031fe507660cf23fd5","tid":790304,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a00bffa234fc46bcba2cb84b20d0874bbf1edbb","tid":790304,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人玩過？<br />\n好好玩架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"依家得啲00後上連登，係咁架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲可能真係90後先玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前我細個成