gmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1035b52da1159933bd1fcbc0f8a78b8f0c0413","tid":790304,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41feaaea3b1fa46cb7ee71e0ffbab6adca55f014","tid":790304,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"啲個真經典<br />\n仲有個賽車賽道（黃色）又係砌到成座山咁高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好鍾意玩呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n砌下砌下又覺得好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3fe4057ac7bded688c703bc68d79bd1e0ce5fc","tid":790304,"uid":93443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"我有<br />\n<br />\n以前用四大天王或麥當勞做主題嘅玩具都好正<br />\n唔知由幾時開始就淨係用其他brand嚟crossover<br />\n明明有能力做自己brand嘅玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d262cdd9f0be84b4e3aad83f44211bf7f4f636","tid":790304,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:23:17.000Z","msg":"以前成日儲啲snoopy用黎打交"},{"pid":"68f266115dad37699b35f6a7173d8abdde540cf3","tid":790304,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f3fe4057ac7bded688c703bc68d79bd1e0ce5fc","tid":790304,"uid":93443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"我有<br />\n<br />\n以前用四大天王或麥當勞做主題嘅玩具都好正<br />\n唔知由幾時開始就淨係用其他brand嚟crossover<br />\n明明有能力做自己brand嘅玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係好好玩<br />\n又訓練小朋友創意又安全玩得<br />\n唔明點解唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家啲垃圾